<title>shén bì bāng zhù 迦南49</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men bù huì gū dān, wǒ men bù huì quē fá, wǒ men de shén bì bāng zhù wǒ men,
 tā míng shì yǐ mǎ nèi lì. tā míng shì yé hé huá yǐ lēi, tā míng shì quán néng de shén,
 wǒ men bù huì gū dān, wǒ men bù huì quē fá, wǒ men de shén bì bāng zhù wǒ men.
 wǒ men de shén bì bāng zhù wǒ men.</lyrics>
</song>